                <p>Farley Road Medical Practice Patient Participation Group Open Meeting Thursday 20th July.</p>
                <p>We are holding an Open Meeting on 20th July 2017 from 6.30 until 8pm at the Selsdon Centre for the Retired (next to Sainsbury and the Library). Come and talk to the Practice and Patient Participation Group members to learn about the way the Practice works.  Contribute your ideas to improve the Practice.</p>
                <p>RSVP to reserve your place to Ms Tracy Ford, Practice Manager on admin@farleymedical.info or call 020 8651 1222 and leave your details.</p>
              </td>
