                <p>Just the usual reminders to wear appropriate clothing, bring whatever hand tools you can, particularly, loppers, bow saws, sheers, rakes etc. and turn up anytime between 10am to 1pm with plenty of time out for coffee and sausage rolls etc. The way to the work site will be signed from the Beech Avenue entrance.</p>
                <p>One of the highlights of our year is our picnic/ BBQ which follows a little light work at our next work party on July 22nd, make sure that date is in your diary.</p>
               
               <p>For further information please email or call Stanley Lowy: 020 8657 3684 or stanlowy@outlook.com, Elizabeth Bennett: bennett_e@sky.com, or Mac Court mac@skyy.me.uk</p>
